	('0D8FuFc5FbmqwzIWuNp6t', 'Main Story Prelude: The Whispers of Horizon', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJ2HmxMAwnMXlcRpYmJ5do0zKw4Qx6PVEtBa9b', '<p><strong>Elara:</strong> <em>(Her voice is a fragile whisper, filled with a yearning for a past she never knew. Her eyes search yours, seeking a spark of empathy)</em> \"You... you possess an aura of curiosity, a thirst for knowledge that\'s almost mythical in these dark times. I believe, perhaps foolishly, that you can help me piece together a shattered story, a story of brilliance, love, and unspeakable loss. The tale of Dr. Aris Thorne and Dr. April Lyra, the architects of the Orb, is buried deep beneath layers of secrets and despair. Will you aid me in unearthing it, even if the truth proves unbearable?\"</p>\n\n<p><strong>Elara:</strong> <em>(Her voice softens as she reminisces)</em> \"Aris... he was a force of nature, a whirlwind of intellect and raw chakra power. They called him a prodigy, a master of manipulation of the land\'s power. But beneath the brilliance, there was a loneliness, a yearning for connection that only April seemed to understand.</p>\n\n<p>April, on the other hand, was a gentle soul, a scientist of rare empathy, a genius in the art of bio-energetics. She saw the potential in everything, in every living being, and sought to harness the land\'s power to the benefit of all. She believed in harmony, in balance. Her intuition was a gift, guiding her to solutions that eluded even Aris\'s sharpest calculations.</p>\n\n<p>Their meeting... it was serendipitous. Aris needed someone to ground his ambition, and April needed someone to fuel her dreams. They met in the Archives, hunched over ancient texts, both seeking a solution to Sechi\'s woes. Sparks flew, not just of scientific innovation, but of something far deeper, far more profound.</p>\n\n<p>The Orb... that was their shared dream, their testament to what humanity could achieve when driven by hope and love. They poured everything into it—their time, their energy, their very souls. But as they delved deeper, as they unlocked powers beyond their comprehension, something twisted. The line between progress and peril blurred, and a shadow crept into their paradise. April began to voice concerns, warnings that Aris, blinded by his ambition, refused to heed. And then... she vanished.\"</p>\n', '\"So the tales are true? They made her the orb so they could control the land. Aris wasn\'t a fool; he knew of their plans. They made her a prisoner for her intellect.\"\n', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 30000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 400000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 10000, \"reward_prestige\": 10000, \"reward_clanpoints\": 3000}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"PmrTxMz8o4aD-jBc2Yc1t\", \"task\": \"pvp_kills\", \"value\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"iREeXHRk600FDBJH5gg2j\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"iREeXHRk600FDBJH5gg2j\", \"task\": \"pvp_kills\", \"value\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"rQ0TEIr4L9x_hU47TnFw4\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"rQ0TEIr4L9x_hU47TnFw4\", \"task\": \"pvp_kills\", \"value\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0,