	('8rK5g22icQUWn0q9fpGSY', '⓸ Revenant\'s Call: Tower of Shadows', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJdb0IVUmP62PI3ciLaYzgVX8FopBADxSrGmvQ', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n    <strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35)\">\n        <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/c60Bk76/Untitled-design-56.gif\" alt=\"Untitled-design-56\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\"><br><br>\n        \n        The journey has led you here—Grimjack’s final bastion of power, the Tower of Shadows.<br>\n        Rising ominously against the darkened sky, the tower pulses with necromantic energy,<br> \n        its foundations woven into the very fabric of death itself. Within these walls, Grimjack<br>\n        prepares to unleash his full fury upon Seichi, his power warping reality and twisting the<br>\n        land around him.\n    </span></strong>\n    <br><br>\n    <strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35)\">\n        As you enter, the air grows thick with malevolence. Four powerful lieutenants stand<br> \n        between you and Grimjack, each one representing a piece of his fractured soul. They<br> \n        all await you, guarding the path to the summit.\n    </span></strong>\n    <br><br>\n    <strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35)\">\n        Each step brings you closer to the heart of Grimjack’s domain. His voice echoes<br> \n        through the darkness, taunting you, daring you to ascend and face him. But this is<br> \n        more than a mere challenge—it is a battle for the very soul of Seichi.\n    </span></strong>\n    <br><br>\n    <strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35)\">\n        The final confrontation draws near. Steel yourself, for once you reach the top of the<br> \n        tower, there will be no turning back. Grimjack waits, and with him, the fate of the<br> \n        living and the dead hangs in the balance.\n    </span></strong>\n    <br><br>\n    <iframe width=\"315\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/qhnjZlfHQ8s?si=1hbyT8_xH-58EJ55\" \n    title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" \n    allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; \n    web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n', 'HAPPY HALLOWEEN FROM ALL OF US AT THENINJA-RPG. THANK YOU SO MUCH FOR SUPPORTING US!', 'D', 10, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 4000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"0B6U_HcjyM2wGwWW9gGxx\", \"kRydr0n1dQpoPqn1LD5oQ\", \"l34MicBdZ4VzdrNFHvNJL\", \"drKYPuUX3-SY51x5RHAWF\", \"qcX4rvjnGBfLdSnHn9-A4\", \"xjkZC0-ETs6Cn454tFSix\", \"EL3MnXz4GeKeKvhNP7Sx0\"], \"reward_money\": 40000, \"reward_badges\": [\"0vVHIhXgGkVwWtNPdSUVO\"], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 400, \"reward_prestige\": 400, \"reward_clanpoints\": 400}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"5KQjfrVoCsntCdDPnUlHP\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJdb0IVUmP62PI3ciLaYzgVX8FopBADxSrGmvQ\", \"sector\": 282, \"latitude\": 2, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 2, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"WELCOME TO THE TOWER OF SHADOWS.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": true, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"nKF3XpKxMUXymh5UNO_-9\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"nKF3XpKxMUXymh5UNO_-9\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJ7zD82EXKPBOUWGyFuM4DlL1v5HNTZhkte0z6\", \"sector\": 282, \"latitude\": 2, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 8, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"Your path to the tower is blocked... The TALISMAN seems to stir in your pack.\", \"opponentAIs\": [\"NdTKQGpXPf