	('akzZPhbrPdyJ-8bKCkSbM', 'The Search for the Kage’s hat pt. 3', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJw7ZBrstT2j854CWbaITZyegfXimvd7s16cO0', '<b>A message from Global ANBU:</b>\n<i> Attention all shinobi of Seichi! The science division of wake island, with help from the global ANBU successfully recovered the first Kage of Silence’s Kage hat. \n\nUpon returning from the far north, we were ambushed by a traveling group of what appeared to be clowns, or jesters of some sort. They attacked in the night and stole the Kage hat from our grasp. And to make matters even worse, they left clues to try and pursue them, almost like this precious artifact is just a mere toy to them and we are all the game! \n\nPlease, come see us at wake island to examine these clues and help discover the whereabouts of these circus shinobi!</i>', '<i>Ah! You’ve recovered it! Thank you so much! This is the third time you’ve saved us and also the third time you’ve recovered such a legendary artifact!! Thank you, THANK YOU! Everyone here at wake island knows how hard you work for the betterment of Seichi. We thank you always. We hope you will accept this payment! And we will be sure to call on you again, young shinobi.</i>', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 10000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 250000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 500, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"jPOar7_aPwTiZNC_goMq7\", \"task\": \"collect_item\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJc132k7SnxBpQqGNDcTHbLmYz8uXAl3oa54ti\", \"sector\": 222, \"latitude\": 11, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"item_name\": \"Killer Clown Riddle 1\", \"longitude\": 1, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Visit the science department to obtain your first clue about the clowns whereabouts.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0,