	('Aubdhg5HVjcHfrxzmj_NZ', '⓵ Revenant\'s Call: Stirring of the Dead', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJHB7l0vQvYURJhgs76VZtf9wxpMa13Cq0iOnr', '<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/H4FmxVF/Untitled-design-50.gif\" alt=\"Untitled-design-50\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <b><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35)\">The Ruins of Samui have become a place of unrest. What was once a peaceful resting ground for the departed is now a source of growing unease. Shadows twist unnaturally, and the long-dead have begun to stir, their slumber interrupted by an unknown force.</span></strong></b>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <b><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35)\">You’ve been sent to uncover the cause of this disturbance. As you step deeper into the ruins, dark energy pulses beneath your feet, and the dead rise more frequently, their minds clouded with the malice of whatever has taken hold here. Your task is simple: investigate the disturbance, battle through the rising dead, and bring back any clues to the village.</span></strong></b>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <b><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35)\">But what lies hidden beneath the earth may be far more dangerous than it appears.</span></strong></b>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <div style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative;\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/l16QmMaXfwc\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; fullscreen\"  style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%;\"><small>Powered by <a href=\"https://embed.tube/embed-code-generator/youtube/\">youtube embed video</a> generator</small></iframe></div>\n</p>\n', 'The air grows thick with malice, a dark pulse rising from the very ground beneath your feet. The talisman you’ve fought so hard to assemble hums with energy—a force far greater than anything you anticipated. Shadows coil and writhe in every corner, as though the land itself is recoiling in fear.\n\nWithout warning, the three fragments reunite, locking into place with a crackling burst of energy. And then… it begins. The once-dormant runes flare to life, their sinister glow casting long, twisted shadows across the ruins. The earth trembles, and a low, guttural laugh echoes from the abyss, growing louder with every heartbeat.\n\nFrom the heart of the shattered earth, a figure rises. Cloaked in darkness, with eyes that burn like the embers of a dying flame. Grimjack—the cursed revenant thought to be sealed away forever—stands before you, his form wreathed in shadows, his power returned.\n\n‘Fools,’ his voice booms, the sound reverberating through your bones. ‘You have done what centuries of warriors could not. You have freed me.’\n\nAround him, the very dead you sought to quell rise once more, an army of shadow and bone, awaiting his command. The ritual you tried to stop is complete, and with it, Grimjack’s reign of terror begins anew. There is no escape, no turning back. Only one question remains—how long will you survive the wrath of the risen?', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 1000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 10000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 100, \"reward_prestige\": 100, \"reward_clanpoints\": 100}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"8-3MDw2YfZsExgt9N8pLt\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJHB7l0vQvYURJhgs76VZtf9wxpMa13Cq0iOnr\", \"sector\": 272, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [\"jiWt92x3ftGxzXZCbmXbB\", \"3K5S1f3bguURTXtIArEkD\"], \"completed\":