	('d3Sn0NqeRP8DUxNaxohz0', 'Whispered Legacy: The Ancient Bamboo Shrine', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJZO9esZqaYQrBIUTu69nkMxWmS4ah0O7LVCp8', '<center><a href=\"https://imgbb.com/\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/BCf7w4D/Untitled-design-10.gif\" alt=\"Untitled-design-10\" border=\"0\"></a>\n<br>\n<p>The head monk of the Ancient Bamboo Shrine stands at the counter with an anxious look in his eyes. His usual calm demeanor has been shattered by a recent, mysterious occurrence. In the dead of night, a scroll appeared within the temple\'s sacred Bamboo Grove, left untouched among the ancient bamboo stalks. Alongside it was a strange tablet, etched with cryptic symbols that glowed under the moonlight.</p>\n<br>\n<p><span style=\"color: #00A36C;\"><i><b>\"The night was still, but when I ventured into the grove at Dusk, this tablet and scroll were waiting for me. The scroll is old, fragile—too delicate to fully reveal its secrets at once,\"</i></b></span> the monk says, his voice low and serious. <span style=\"color: #00A36C;\"><i><b>\"This tablet, however, glows faintly under the moon, revealing strange symbols I’ve never seen before. I know it’s the key to deciphering the riddle hidden in the scroll.\"</i></b></span></p>\n<br>\n<p>He hands you the <b>Lunar Cipher Tablet</b> but hesitates before continuing.</p>\n<br>\n<p><span style=\"color: #00A36C;\"><b><i>\"The scroll itself is fragmented. The spirits of the grove only allow us to part with one section at a time. After you find each treasure, you must return to the Bamboo Shrine to receive the next piece of the riddle. Patience and caution are your allies. The path ahead is dangerous, and the treasures are guarded fiercely.\"</b></i></span></p>\n<br>\n<p>With the tablet in hand, you are tasked with retrieving the first fragment of the riddle from the Ancient Bamboo Shrine and solving the mystery of the forgotten treasures.</p>\n\n<br><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/fxkWrNq/Untitled-design-13.gif\" alt=\"Untitled-design-13\" 