	('g3F4j5j8CjNTIWKMfe4Et', 'The Path to Shine', 'https://utfs.io/f/a1e1fadd-eecc-4b01-99d4-d5de59352b44-yiu9ce.webp', 'Greetings, traveler! Welcome to my beloved village of Shine, blessed by the light of Amaterasu herself. Our history is as radiant as the sun that guides us. I have lived here all my life and know every ray of light that touches this sacred ground. To truly understand the essence of Shine, you must walk the path of our ancestors, who sought the warmth and light of the sun. Join me on this journey to uncover the glorious story of our home.<br><br>\n\nBegin your journey at the Ravaged Sands. This area was the initial settlement of our sun-devoted ancestors before a mysterious climate change forced them to move. Our ancestors\' journey began here, where they hoped to establish a community under the sun. However, the sudden climate change turned this area into a land of constant rain and clouds, pushing them to seek a new home.<br><br>\n\n<p>Next, make your way to the Shining Dunes. This discovery was a turning point for our people, offering them the sunlit land they had been searching for. This place was instantly recognized as their new home, perfectly aligned with their beliefs.<br><br>\n\n<p>Continue to the Southern Desert. This region, with its harsh climate and unforgiving terrain, tested our people\'s resilience and devotion to the sun.<br><br>\n\nProceed to the Northern Desert, where our people harnessed the power of the sun to transform the arid land into a thriving community.<br><br>\n\nFinally, journey to Sunrise Canyon, where the first rays of Amaterasu\'s light bless our village each day. While Shine is built on the Shining Dunes, the best sunrises are seen from here, symbolizing our unwavering devotion to the sun and the divine favor that led to the establishment of Shine\n', 'Congratulations, shinobi! You\'ve successfully completed your mission in Shine, tracing our sun-devoted ancestors\' path. From the Ravaged Sands, where they faced adversity, to the Shining Dunes, their new home. You braved the Southern Desert\'s harshness and saw the Northern Desert\'s transformation. Finally, you witnessed the divine light at Sunrise Canyon. Your dedication and perseverance have honored Shine\'s legacy. Well done! — Tenjiro Sensei', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 1000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"5kN43XOd-VYuRTQZ8OW-B\"], \"reward_money\": 1000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"X9Jui0hC8aWvacA0-RrC6\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/afde1b31-6a0b-46ea-9cad-b398c867d7ac-kpt8fh.webp\", \"sector\": 259, \"latitude\": 1, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 7, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"\", \"opponentAIs\": [\"Tpeyj29qZmwphSIpNcL0P\"], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"opponent_name\": \"Hibiki no Seirei\", \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fled from the opponent\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"JtPCTw9BboJEA_xWdHUrF\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": false, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"JtPCTw9BboJEA_xWdHUrF\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/89e9f77c-8287-45de-a860-f95011b537c5-nud4fo.webp\", \"sector\": 83, \"latitude\": 11, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 8, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"\", \"opponentAIs\": [\"yWmaHQTYMsvqZpChkoqKz\"], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_ite