	('JObMMKATKcfCotGUMU4gk', 'The Search for the Kage’s Hat', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJ7v5N8FXKPBOUWGyFuM4DlL1v5HNTZhkte0z6', '<p>Hello again! Thank you for coming. As you may have heard since uncovering the Diamond Dagger, the historical workers here at Wake Island, and even myself as their chief were wondering; what other ancient items lay waiting to be rediscovered again in our lands of Seichi? The answer we sought in our various texts revealed that there were many items lost, over many years, battles, and architectural changes. </p><br>\n\n<p>We have been combing through all of our texts about previous eras in Seichi, and we realized that there are in fact many missing items from those times! If you don’t mind helping, we would like you to help us uncover those items over time! It will be long, and difficult to find these legendary lost items, but we believe you have the skills to help us, like before!</p><br>\n\n<p>First we would like you to attempt to track down the hat of the First Kage of Konoki. Perhaps you should travel to Tsukimori and the surrounding areas, to see if there are any clues or remnants left behind that can help guide you.”</p> <br>\n', 'Unbelievable! We knew it was out there! And after all this time… thank you!! We were right to place our faith in you! We will store this in our sacred vault in the hopes that one day it may be put on display here at wake island for all to see, and hopefully learn something about the history of Seichi. Please be sure to return, as we will be working hard at uncovering move trails for legendary items for you to gather for us!', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 2000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 100, \"reward_clanpoints\": 100}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"92oYfkkHRfbpZwK19knp9\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJ7v5N8