	('pzNs8-2ROre8OWb-ya2ND', 'Legend of the Diamond Dagger ', 'https://utfs.io/f/16d54300-55ee-4fd3-ab9a-17495c0d0611-t483a3.webp', 'During the Third Era\'s time of peace, a magnificent discovery was unearthed: diamonds. The excavation of diamonds brought not only wealth but also many technological advancements. Many villages sought to gather as many as they could to enhance armor, weapons, and gain prowess and strength over one another. One village, above all else, grew extremely jealous: Silence. They feared being left behind due to their lack of diamonds as a resource near their village. They decided that even in a time of peace, allowing other villages these advancements would eventually lead to their eradication. So they plotted against the village with the most natural resources, including diamonds.<br><br>\n\nThe Village of Shine.<br><br>\n\nThey sent a lone ninja into the night with a single mission: find and locate blueprints or prototype weapons and armor made with diamonds and steal them.<br><br>\n\nLegend tells that the mission, although carefully planned, ended in failure. The legendary prototype weapon of Shine, the Diamond Dagger, was successfully stolen from its home, but a silent alarm was tripped, sending Shine\'s forces after the ninja. Knowing his certain demise, the ninja did the only thing he could: destroy the prototype. If Silence couldn’t have this advancement in technology, nobody would.<br><br>\n\nChanneling his chakra into his fist and sword, he slammed against the shimmering weapon with all his might, each blow glistening in the moonlight as he ran. Finally, after exhausting himself, the weapon was broken into three pieces. Hearing the enemy close behind, he thought quickly. Using the last of his chakra, he sent the pieces flying as far away as he could, breathing a sigh of relief knowing that no village would gain an edge in military strength due to advancements in weaponry—at least, not for now. He closed his eyes as his enemies caught up to him. He was captured and executed the next day as a warning to all who dared to infiltrate Shine.<br><br>\n\nNobody has been able to collect these pieces, until perhaps now. A clue has been found, and perhaps a small trail. Please collect this ancient artifact for us.”<br><br>', 'With these pieces finally collected, the tale of the Diamond Dagger can officially be immortalized in time. No longer a myth, but reality. Thank you for helping collect these pieces of the dagger, that hold so much history within them about our beloved land of Seichi. We couldn’t have done it without you! Please take this as a token of our gratitude!', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 500, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"s9OtX-WvIHkJjUtJh52Ji\", \"P8blSysgMtpciGgo_ZMMl\"], \"reward_money\": 10000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 100, \"reward_prestige\": 100, \"reward_clanpoints\": 20}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"bBPVuX288xAyAJpJHK4QI\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/16d54300-55ee-4fd3-ab9a-17495c0d0611-t483a3.webp\", \"sector\": 292, \"latitude\": 1, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 0, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"We\'ve overheard some travelers talking about a shimmering stone deep in the mountains! Please investigate the mountains of Seichi to learn more. \", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": true, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"jXWcFcN5QSt4M05VFRnhc\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"jXWcFcN5QSt4M05VFRnhc\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/8b32ff62-21ed-443e-b1f7-7095b27198db-2d72.png\", \"sector\": 292, \"latitude\": 8, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"l