	('q8csaLhChyxRgnOs89cKi', 'A Call for Aid from the Grovetender', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJu1512CyJLoOFkrcn4gxSwCfEQ9eMNXZlG8bI', 'A Call for Aid from the Grovetender \n<br> Something is wrong in the Shining Expanse. The Sandworms, ancient beasts that sleep beneath the dunes, have begun to rampage. They tear through the land without reason, destroying everything in their path.\n<br> \n<br> I am The Grovetender, guardian of this land. I do not know what has disturbed the Sandworms, but their destruction is spreading. Sunny the Tree, the oldest and most sacred tree in the desert, is in danger. If it falls, the balance of life here will be lost, and the village of Shine will suffer.\n<br> <br> \n I cannot stop this alone. I call upon the Global Anbu—warriors of skill and courage—to help defend the tree and uncover the cause of this disaster. Time is running out, and the sands do not wait for anyone.\n<br> \n<br> Will you answer?\n<br> \n<br> —Grovetender of Shine\n', 'As the waves crash against the shores of Wake Island, the silence feels almost unreal after the chaos of the desert. The battle with the Alpha Sandworm is over, but its memory lingers—each scar, each grain of sand still clinging to your gear, a reminder of what you faced. The Grovetender’s words echo in your mind, a mix of gratitude and warning, knowing the balance of the dunes has shifted.', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 0, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [\"eUWHPdGiydKJooFs-sCc_\"], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"TMcCih8jev_ABTSFgqqXY\", \"task\": \"collect_item\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJ2HtT5XmnMXlcRpYmJ5do0zKw4Qx6PVEtBa9b\", \"sector\": 83, \"latitude\": 9, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"item_name\": \"1st Map piece\", \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Collect first map piece