	('rDN4CT1NoWswUk1zCb8Gq', 'The Path of a Shinobi ', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJxGgCsmWZsq9k0Von5rUfP6OgQ2TyptCKHS4u', '<p>\"The Mortal King,\" Haki begins, his voice echoing in the stillness, \"is no mere legend.<br>He is a celestial being whose presence alone disturbs the balance of our world.<br>He walks the line between divinity and mortality, wielding powers that can reshape the very fabric of Seichi.\"</p>\n\n<p>He gestures toward a map spread across the table.<br>Marked upon it are several locations where traces of the Mortal King\'s presence have been detected—places where the laws of nature have been twisted, and chaos has ensued.<br>Wildfire erupts in the Shining Dunes without cause; eternal storms rage in Current\'s Whirling Valley; ice forms in Glacier\'s Frozen Highlands, not of Kuraokami\'s making, but of something far more sinister.</p>\n\n<p>\"Your mission is to track these disturbances,\" Haki continues, his eyes locking onto each Chunin in turn.<br>\"Investigate the traces left behind by this celestial figure.<br>Find out what he seeks, and most importantly, prevent him from reaching the Monarch Powers—ancient forces that, if combined with his celestial abilities, could plunge our world into irreversible darkness.\"</p>\n\n<p>The Chunin exchange glances, their resolve hardening.<br>Each of them carries the weight of their village on their shoulders, but none falter.<br>They understand the stakes—failure is not an option.</p>\n\n<p>Haki pauses, allowing the gravity of his words to sink in.<br>Then, with a final nod, he concludes, \"You will face not just the Mortal King, but those who serve him—beings of great power and deception.<br>Trust in your training, in each other, and in Seichi.<br>Dismissed.\"</p>\n', '<p>They have won, but the victory is bittersweet.<br>Haki, once their leader, now lies defeated and broken.<br>The Monarch Powers remain beyond their reach, but Seichi is safe—for now.</p>\n\n<p>As they make their way back to the surface, the Chunin know that their journey is far from over.<br>The world may never know of their sacrifice, of the betrayal they faced, or of the celestial judgment that looms over them.<br>But they carry the lessons of this mission with them, a reminder that even in the darkest moments, honor and duty must guide their path.</p>\n\n<p>And somewhere, far beyond the mortal realm, the Mortal King watches, waiting for the day when the balance of Seichi will be tested once more. The monarch is coming and this fragile peace will be broken.</p>\n', 'B', 48, NULL, 'exam', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 0, \"reward_rank\": \"JONIN\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 400000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"ag583IXd8BSIAMKw0JUGR\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJxGgCsmWZsq9k0Von5rUfP6OgQ2TyptCKHS4u\", \"sector\": 83, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The team departs the Global ANBU headquarters under the cover of night, each Chunin heading towards their assigned location. Their paths will take them through treacherous terrains\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"y63xfuXOtTOIPM7s5ajWM\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"Search the Area for the deity that is causing the disturbances. \", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"y63xfuXOtTOIPM7s5ajWM\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/89e9f77c-8287-45de-a860-f95011b537c5-nud4fo.webp\", \"sector\": 83, \"latitude\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 10, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1