xtObjectiveId\": \"3J1axtyUtyZ-UIZTROt6h\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"As the servant falls, defeated, the winds begin to calm, and the valley grows quiet. The Chunin stand amidst the ruins of their battle, exhausted but victorious. They have uncovered a crucial piece of the puzzle, a revelation that will bring them one step closer to the Mortal King himself. The Map Points to the Frozen Highlands\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": true, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"3J1axtyUtyZ-UIZTROt6h\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJxGgCsmWZsq9k0Von5rUfP6OgQ2TyptCKHS4u\", \"sector\": 307, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The journey of the Chunin has led them to an ancient ruin in the ironwood forest, a place forgotten by time and untouched by the living. The air is heavy with the presence of the celestial being known as the Mortal King. The ground beneath them hums with energy as they enter the final chamber, a vast space carved from stone and adorned with cryptic symbols that seem to shift and change with every glance. In the center of the chamber, a massive altar looms, pulsing with an otherworldly light. The Chunin can feel the power radiating from it, a force so overwhelming that it threatens to tear apart the fabric of reality itself. They know that this is where the Mortal King plans to unlock the Monarch Powers—a moment that could change the fate of Seichi forever. But as they prepare to confront the celestial being, something feels off. Haki, their enigmatic leader, stands before the altar, his back turned to them. His figure, usually so composed and commanding, now seems shrouded in a dark, almost malevolent energy. One of the Chunin speaks up, their voice laced with concern. \\\"Haki, what are you 