	('simJf04-Kr2mHZOCKf0ym', '[Path of Crimson] [Part II: The Ember Trail]', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJC5oYhI26OYrIJuNP1pvSyz29edFtKbngjRcA', '<center><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xsDT5vP/DALL-E-2025-01-24-20-56-53-A-high-quality-pixel-art-scene-set-on-Wake-Island-during-a-serene-dusk-Th.webp\" alt=\"DALL-E-2025-01-24-20-56-53-A-high-quality-pixel-art-scene-set-on-Wake-Island-during-a-serene-dusk-Th\" border=\"0\"><br>\n<i>The sky glows with the colors of twilight as Dusk stands at the edge of Wake Island, his golden scarf flickering in the breeze. His gaze is distant, his expression thoughtful, but when you approach, he turns to you with a faint smirk.</i><br>  \n<br>\n<b>\"Ah, there you are. I thought perhaps the embers had swallowed you, but you’re too stubborn for that, aren’t you?\"</b><br>  \n<br>\n<i>His smirk fades, and he gestures toward a map spread across a nearby stone. The parchment is old, singed at the edges, with three locations marked:</i> <b>The Flamebinding Altar, Infernal Pool, and Ember Crossroads.</b><br>  \n<br>\n<b>\"The Black Maw’s flames burn hotter along the Ember Trail. This isn’t just another raid—they’re targeting sacred sites. These seals aren’t just relics. They’re bindings, meant to hold dangerous energies. If they succeed in breaking them, the fires won’t stop with these sites.\"</b><br>  \n<br>\n<i>He looks back at you, his tone quieter but heavier with meaning.</i><br>  \n<br>\n<b>\"Seals like these don’t just break—they shatter. Shadows twist, fire spreads, and what’s unleashed doesn’t go back easily. You’ll need to stop them. Follow the trail, disrupt their rituals, and bring me anything you find.\"</b><br>  \n<br>\n<i>He pauses, his fiery scarf shifting slightly, as though caught in an unseen current.</i><br>  \n<br>\n<b>\"And be careful. What the Maw touches leaves marks that don’t fade.\"</b><br>  \n<br>\n<i>As he hands you the map, his eyes meet yours, the intensity behind them unmistakable.</i><br>  \n<br>\n<b>\"Go. Fire destroys, but it also reveals. Just don’t let it consume you.\"</b><br>  \n<br>\n<i>His gaze lingers on the horizon for a moment before he turns back to the village, his scarf glowing faintly in the dimming light.</i></center>', NULL, 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 3000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"wR2M9GgcFckOXCqLBcfzl\"], \"reward_money\": 100000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"O--tDk05jdn77u3iK7Yga\", \"task\": \"collect_item\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJOGKW5KPVHevxIThUauQkGJEBY3D2cPqy8f5s\", \"sector\": 222, \"latitude\": 9, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"item_name\": \"Ember Trail Parchment\", \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Dusk hands you a map. Make sure to read it over. The Flamebinding Altar is your first destination.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"collectItemIds\": [\"ju0pImmz5H0D0eVTyGnJ0\"], \"nextObjectiveId\": \"cm91P192c_85rADr5Yuj6\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"delete_on_complete\": false, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"cm91P192c_85rADr5Yuj6\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJC5oYhI26OYrIJuNP1pvSyz29edFtKbngjRcA\", \"sector\": 16, \"latitude\": 13, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 1, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You stumble across something you... might have wish you hadn\'t. They saw you.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": true, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"2Dq2ZNyxVLMSRWtE8mnpw\", \"reward_prestige