	('T8T7YKNszDr6z6IgzciTY', '[Path of Crimson] [Part I: The Sunset Road]', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJmyPmACHE4IMO5Goa7cgLxPJ0VC6lU8vbt1Ap', '<center><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vXYbdLp/WORKSPACE-11.png\" alt=\"WORKSPACE-11\" border=\"0\"><br>\n<i>You step into the Administration Building at Wake Island. The air is heavy with the scent of burning incense, mingling with faint traces of ash. Dusk is waiting by the window, his glowing eyes fixed on the horizon. His golden scarf billows gently, though there’s no wind.</i>\n<br>\n<br><b>\"Ah, there you are. I’ve been waiting. The Sunset Road is burning—quite literally. Caravans have been destroyed, cargo vanished, and the culprits remain in the shadows.”\n<br>\n<br>“This isn’t random. It reeks of the Black Maw. They don’t simply attack—they calculate, they take, and they leave nothing but ash in their wake.”\n<br>\n<br>“I need you to investigate. Follow the trail. Find out what they’re after. And if you run into resistance...”</b>\n<br>\n<br><i>Dusk smirks, his fiery scarf shifting with the breeze.</i>\n<br>\n<br><b>“Well, let’s just say they won’t be calculating much after you’re done.”\n<br>\n<br>“Start at the caravan site. You’ll find it near Sector 338. And remember—anything you find may burn, but it won’t destroy the truth.”</b>\n<br><br></center>', 'See you in seven days. ~ DUSK ~', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 2500, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 100000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"V7XX7vFeBswNzGI_6XSI2\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJmyPmACHE4IMO5Goa7cgLxPJ0VC6lU8vbt1Ap\", \"sector\": 338, \"latitude\": 0, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 0, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocat