	('TbDplr6b5y_EEAe_d-PVY', '⓶ Revenant\'s Call: Shadow\'s Reach', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJnpydZFmojJ0EqeDCvBrNmZaXVdY97gSpOWiA', '\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/TtbpRcS/Untitled-design-51.gif\" alt=\"Image\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\">\n    <p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 126, 35);\">\n    Seichi trembles under a growing shadow. Grimjack has returned—revived by the very hands that sought to destroy him—and his dark influence spreads like a sickness, corrupting the very heart of the land. The skies darken, and the once vibrant fields and forests now twist and shiver beneath the weight of his power. Villages once filled with life fall silent, their inhabitants fleeing as the shadows crawl ever closer.<br><br>\n    From the Ruins of Horizon, an ancient and sacred place now desecrated by necromantic energy, tendrils of dark magic reach out like claws, creeping across the landscape. This darkness is not random—it is focused, purposeful. And with each passing moment, its hold tightens.<br><br>\n    As you move through Seichi, the signs are clear: scattered remnants of villages lie in disarray, and the forest spirits—once guardians of these lands—hover restlessly, their forms distorted by Grimjack’s curse. The Ruins of Horizon pulse with blue and purple light, casting long, sinister shadows that stretch across the earth. The corruption there is thick, like poison in the air, and the whispers of the past seem to echo from every shattered stone.<br><br>\n    But this darkness is not absolute. There are secrets hidden within these ruins, mysteries that must be uncovered if the curse is to be broken. Somewhere within this chaos lies the source of the encroaching evil—an ancient power that must be confronted and stopped before it spreads further.<br><br>\n    The path ahead is uncertain, and Seichi’s fate hangs in the balance. It’s time to face the consequences of your actions. \n    </span></strong></p>\n</div>\n<!-- Centered, Square YouTube Video at the Bottom -->\n<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; margin-top: 20px; height: 300px;\">\n    <iframe width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dIYjx2lALHY\" \n    frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n', 'With the Master Reanimator lying defeated at your feet, the necromantic energy in the air begins to wane. You step forward and collect the final scroll from his grasp. Its ancient runes reveal a chilling truth: Grimjack’s plan was never to raise just an army—it’s to spread his curse across the land, starting with the Reanimation Chamber you’ve learned about.\n\nAs you read, the shadows twist unnaturally, and a cold realization dawns. This fight was just a prelude. Grimjack’s true power is growing, and now you know where his next move will strike.\n\nYour path is clear, but the shadows grow deeper, and the weight of what comes next presses on your shoulders.', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 2000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [\"kRydr0n1dQpoPqn1LD5oQ\", \"l34MicBdZ4VzdrNFHvNJL\", \"drKYPuUX3-SY51x5RHAWF\"], \"reward_money\": 30000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 200, \"reward_prestige\": 200, \"reward_clanpoints\": 200}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"wRcWKSwFrCUKWtULzeTwQ\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJnpydZFmojJ0EqeDCvBrNmZaXVdY97gSpOWiA\", \"sector\": 281, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [\"jiWt92x3ftGxzXZCbmXbB\", \"3K5S1f3bguURTXtIArEkD\"], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 10, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Back to the Ruins of Horizon.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"