	('WavQUdfdJEVR63EqX4WvY', 'Echoes of Turmoil: The Spirits\' Frenzy', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJprA1kQbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D', '<center><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/dkVYx4T/Foxgirl-1.png\"> <br><p>Before you stands <strong>Senka, the Spirit Whisperer</strong>, a striking figure with fox-like features that give her an otherworldly grace. Her hair, streaked with white, cascades in waves over her shoulders, and her amber eyes glimmer like molten gold. As she speaks, her voice is calm and measured, almost hypnotic, drawing you into her words.</p>\n<br>\n<p><em><strong>\"For centuries, the spiritual energy of Seichi has flowed like a tranquil river, connecting all life and maintaining the delicate balance between realms. But now, that harmony is unraveling. Reports flood in from across the land: spirits vanishing without a trace, while others—once benevolent—wreak havoc with unnatural aggression. Villages live in fear, haunted by whispers of strange, luminous crystals that have begun to emerge in dark, forgotten places.\"</strong></em></p>\n<br>\n<p>Her fox ears twitch at the faintest sounds, and her bushy tail, adorned with silver tips, sways gently behind her. She pauses for a moment, her keen eyes studying you, making it clear that she misses nothing. The faint shimmer of the patterns on her flowing robes catches the moonlight.</p>\n<br>\n<p><em><strong>\"The Global Anbu believes a sinister force is meddling with the fabric of life and death, something far beyond the natural order. This disturbance echoes the ancient tale of Aria, the first to bond with the celestial crystals. Her bloodline has always stood as protectors of the balance, but even their strength might not be enough to face what lies ahead.\"</strong></em></p>\n<br>\n<p>A crystal pendant hangs from her neck, its glow seems to resonate with her very spirit, a testament to her deep connection to the realms she protects. Senka\'s serene demeanor belies the fierce determination burning within her to restore balance to Seichi.</p>\n<br>\n<p><em><strong>\"Your mission is urgent: investigate the disturbances, track the source of the chaos, and uncover the truth behind the corrupted spirits and mysterious crystals. Beware—what you find may be tied to Seichi’s deepest secrets, and the choices you make will shape the fate of the realms.\"</strong></em></p>\n<br>\n<p>With a final, meaningful look, she nods, her voice carrying the weight of the quest ahead. <em><strong>\"I believe in your strength and wisdom. Go now, and may the spirits guide you.\"</strong></em></p> </center>\n', 'You return from the field, shaken but alive, with unsettling news. The glowing crystal beings you encountered radiated an unnatural energy, drawing spirits close to trap them and twisting their essence into aggression. The attacks felt deliberate, like a defense mechanism protecting something sinister. It’s clear these crystals aren’t natural, and someone—or something—is behind their creation. ', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 5000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 200000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 200, \"reward_prestige\": 400, \"reward_clanpoints\": 150}, \"objectives\": []}', 1, '2025-01-31 06:06:00.814', '2025-01-31 06:06:00.814', NULL, NULL, 1, 100, NULL, 1, 1, 'none', NULL),
