	('Xjkw7D3QZorrOkvyI6rDS', 'The Cute Crimson Cloak', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJwZ6wNCT2j854CWbaITZyegfXimvd7s16cO0h', '<p>A cheerful young girl named Akane, known for her cute crimson cloak, must journey to her grandmother\'s house deep within the forest to deliver sake, mochi, and medicine. The villagers warn you of recent attacks and creatures terrorizing the forest. Strange occurrences and ominous howls have been heard, making the villagers too afraid to help.Akane, however, remains oblivious to the danger and insists on completing her task. \n<br>\nAs a skilled ninja, your mission is to escort Akane through the treacherous forest, defend her from any threats, and ensure a proper delivery of the goods at the <i>end of the forest.</i></p>', '<p>The battle in the Forests End finishes with the defeat of the fearsome okuri okami. Though Akane’s grandmother could not be saved, the forest is now free from the terror that once lurked within. The young girl, still clutching her crimson cloak, looks up at you with tear-filled eyes but manages a soft smile of gratitude.\n<br>\n“Thank you... for everything,” she whispers. Though her loss is great, Akane\'s courage shines through, and she knows that, with your help, she will return home safely.</p>', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 2000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 150000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 100, \"reward_prestige\": 200, \"reward_clanpoints\": 100}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"vnp2t8T_z8xNpw0LSctVd\", \"task\": \"collect_item\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJ0zV093grYldRWJcD6vE10SjNsXHeA9pVMfQi\", \"sector\": 305, \"latitude\": 6, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"item_name\": \"Akane\", \"longitude\": 14, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Pick up and escort Akane\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_