	('zLyJ40btgeIODDge9w3Hg', 'The Night Of The Undead', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJdbZ1dgpP62PI3ciLaYzgVX8FopBADxSrGmvQ', 'Just outside the village of Shine, a rugged field lies bordered by dense forest, transformed each year into a haunting battleground under the light of the moon. Villagers gather, crafting eerie structures with flickering lights and rolling fog, setting the stage for one of the most chilling nights of the year.<br><br>\n\nThe night isn’t just a festival—it’s a tribute. As darkness falls, the atmosphere thickens with tension, and participants prepare to face horrors that once threatened the land. This is <b>the Night of the Undead</b>, a moment where past battles are honored, and new ones are fought in the shadows of the forest.<br><br>\n\nThe Night of the Undead is not just a test of courage—it’s a tribute to Goah’s bravery and a reminder that, even when darkness rises, the strength of the human spirit will always shine through. Prepare for a night where the undead rise, and only the strongest will endure.\n', 'The Night of the Undead is not just a celebration of Goah’s bravery, but a reminder that even in the face of overwhelming darkness, the light of the sun—and the strength of the human spirit—will always prevail.\n\nAnd so, the legend of Goah Way, the sun praiser and wandering sage, continued. His battle against the undead became a symbol of hope, inspiring future generations to face the darkness with courage and light.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 2000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 300000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"2qv2Eqeg5FqgXRdT66Vsm\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJdbZ1dgpP62PI3ciLaYzgVX8FopBADxSrGmvQ\", \"sector\": 66, \"latitude\": 1, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 0, \"r