	('zsfwyoMXxL3stLVS4ZEum', 'The Search for the Kage’s hat Part 2', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJT22jdj5IU29dZYJPoOKSh5vmlqatMub3EigH', '<p>“Thank you for coming so quickly. We are sorry to call you here so urgently and without warning, but we have uncovered the possible whereabouts of the lost Kage of Samui’s hat! While excavating deep in the ice for ancient relics, we came upon this ancient time of ice. It doesn’t melt, and is as heavy as 20 pounds of steel. When heat makes contact with it, a message appears: </p> <br>\n\n<p>“Fearing revolution, it was hidden. The powers untold, if fallen into the wrong hands. Only the sacred shrines of the Kage can unveil the truth. Find these hidden shrines, vanquish the shrine guardians, and uncover a relic thought lost forever.\"</p>\n', '<p>“Unbelievable! Another seemingly lost relic of Seichi, collected again. Without you, the legendary tales of these hats would remain just that. A legend. You are bringing the legends to life for all of Seichi! We are all closer with our nation and its history, thanks to you. Please, accept these rewards as our thanks.\"</p>', 'D', 1, NULL, 'event', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 3000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 125000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 500, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"reward_clanpoints\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"2sEhP9hfyYqkUdOxmRj_R\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJT22jdj5IU29dZYJPoOKSh5vmlqatMub3EigH\", \"sector\": 25, \"latitude\": 3, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 12, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"“The first shrine lies under desert skies in.”\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"cUHNLNX0rzeU4jNTQq2Lc\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"attackers_chance\": 0, \"reward_clanpoi